        "from": "OrderEnrichmentService",
        "to": "InventoryService",
        "status": "broken",
        "issue": "InventoryService p99 alone is 800ms, which already exceeds the 500ms inbound timeout. Even if this were the ONLY downstream call, p99 requests would fail. This call is made third in the sequential chain, so by the time it starts (~350ms in at best), only ~150ms remain before the upstream caller disconnects."
